public class Operator
extends java.lang.Object

SEIG Java Operator class.

SEIG uses the MTJ Java library (matrix-toolkits-java) and Netlib Java (netlib-java) for numerical linear algebra and matrix computations.

Author:
Rico Argentati

operatorAction

public no.uib.cipr.matrix.DenseMatrix operatorAction(no.uib.cipr.matrix.DenseMatrix X)
This method applies the operator to a dense input matrix and returns a dense matrix. The method operatorAction can be overwritten to provide any matrix block vector multiply or any operation desired by the user as long as X is returned.
